  "text": "RNA extraction and Northern blot analyses were performed as described previously [CITATION_1] . Equal amounts of total RNA (30 g) were loaded onto agarose gels for electrophoresis, and the gels were blotted and probed with an RNA probe specific for qde-2 or dcl-2. The rRNA levels were shown by the ethidium bromide-stained agarose gels.",
